description:
Elf your friends and yourself with Elf Ur Face! Select or take a new picture of your friends and family, and decorate them with holiday stickers. Be sure to get in the Christmas spirit, and send everyone the elfing fun via email, Facebook, and Twitter!

FEATURES:
- Select an image from your photo library or take a new picture to decorate!
- Gorgeous elfing stickers and Christmas themed stickers!
- Save your artwork to your device's photo library!
- Share your work of art with your friends and family through email, Facebook, and Twitter!

*******************************************************
Don't forget to scroll down on the stickers page to see more stickers!
*******************************************************

Please note: A network connection is required to share your artwork, and to download new stickers. You do not need a network connection in order to save your artwork to your device's photo library though.
releaseNotes: More stickers, more features, more holiday cheer!  Happy Holidays, Merry Christmas!
